data.description: Gorgeously updated home on OVER half an acre within Robinson ISD!! This move-in ready 2,189 sqft home has a wonderful open-concept floor plan with 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a cozy living room with a wood burning fireplace, a decked out kitchen, a huge walk in pantry and a sunroom that leads to the back porch.  The kitchen is a dream!!! The neutral color palette, stunning cabinetry and stainless steel appliances makes for an amazing space to cook and entertain.  This home has lots of upgrades inside and out that even includes having a less than 2 year old roof.  More exterior features include a large workshop, great-sized covered porch, a fire pit area and plenty of room to roam on the massive lot.  This turn-key home is ready for you to call it home in a great neighborhood and school district and a bonus….You are just minutes to town and all that Robinson and Waco have to offer!
